############################

- Download the branch from github page:

    $ cd DEVELOPMENT_PATH
    $ git clone git@github.com:OpenCode/geany-python-good-code.git

- Move in plugin path and compile it:

    $ cd geany-python-good-code
    $ gcc -c python-good-code.c -fPIC `pkg-config --cflags geany` 
    $ gcc python-good-code.o -o python-good-code.so -shared `pkg-config --libs geany` 
    $ cp python-good-code.so GEANY_PLUGIN_PATH/python-good-code.so
